abstract: Texas Christian defeats Brigham Young, 38-28, in college football action.
snippet: Texas Christian quarterback Casey Pachall threw two touchdown passes, and the Horned Frogs built a big first-half lead over visiting Brigham Young en route to a 38-28 win.
